      "question": "Evaluate: $\\frac{\\tan 65^\\circ}{\\cot 25^\\circ} + \\sin^2 30^\\circ$.",
      "answer": "1.25",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "Use the complementary angle identity $\\tan(90^\\circ - \\theta) = \\cot \\theta$ to simplify the first term.",
